# Local dev process data — safety net.
# Real/customer process files are loaded at runtime via "Load folder" and must
# never be committed. Only the empty index.json skeleton is tracked here; the
# shipped demo dataset lives in data/demo/ (tracked).
/niju-ichi/data/processes/*.json
!/niju-ichi/data/processes/index.json
